Transitions:
CSS transitions allows you to change property values smoothly, over a given duration.

When we move from one styling to another styling without any complex process then we can call it as transition

Transition is child/subset of Animation(styling changes from one to another - complex)

Moving from one state of styling to another state of styling

Transition properties: 
transition
transition-delay
transition-duration
transition-property
transition-timing-function

shorthand notation :
